        <item>
            <id>https://www.ithome.com/0/873/808.htm</id>
            <title>京东冰洗超级国补周正式开启，小天鹅滚筒洗衣机 1449 → 911 元再降价</title>
            <link>https://www.ithome.com/0/873/808.htm</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://www.ithome.com/0/873/808.htm</guid>
            <pubDate></pubDate>
            <updated>Thu, 07 Aug 2025 13:49:03 GMT</updated>
                
                
